Overall, this dream may highlight a mix of emotions, including nostalgia, uncertainty, adaptability, and the need for security. It could be a reflection of your subconscious mind processing past experiences, present challenges, and hopes for the future.
title: "Inconvenient Checkout and Surprising Encounters: A Nostalgic Supermarket Dream"

dream: I had a dream I was with a group of people and we were doing activities together my assigned work shedules were very good I was quite happy with it but there were some other people who did not like their shedules as there was not enough play time. A friend of mine who was making soups and juices did not like his shedule so I told him that it is important to have joy in the work then it doesn’t really matter how long it takes. I was happy to see he found a way to enjoy himself . He had placed his blender high up and threw in the fruits like it was a basket ball net and he enjoyed himself a lot. At some point I discovered an area I had not seen before and there was a stall with food and I went to sit there. I saw they had brussel waffles, a thing I enjoyed as a kid. But as a vegan I can’t have them anymore as they have milk in them and sometimes even eggs. I thought to myself why not give myself the pleasure to have one. When the waffle came out of the iron it was quite burned and when I wanted to pay my money was also burned. The woman asked if I had another note to pay with as she could not accept this then I said no and realized that it’s a divine intervention as I should not break my vegan lifestyle to just indulge into something that isn’t good for me
interpretation:
This dream may indicate a desire for balance and joy in your daily activities. The positive experience of having a good work schedule reflects your satisfaction in the tasks and responsibilities you currently have. However, the presence of others who are dissatisfied with their schedules suggests the importance of finding joy and enjoyment in your work, regardless of the time it takes. You offering your friend advice on finding joy in his work demonstrates your understanding of the importance of maintaining a positive attitude.

The scene with the friend using the blender creatively symbolizes finding unconventional ways to enjoy and have fun, even in mundane or repetitive tasks. This may suggest that you have the ability to inject joy and creativity into your work or daily routines, helping you find fulfillment.

The discovery of a new area with food and the presence of brussel waffles, a childhood favorite that you can no longer enjoy due to your vegan lifestyle, corresponds to a conflict between indulgence and adhering to your beliefs or principles. The burned waffle and money in the dream represent a negative outcome or consequence of going against your values.

Overall, this dream may remind you of the importance of finding joy in your work, maintaining a positive attitude, and staying true to your principles, even in situations where it may be tempting to compromise. It encourages you to find creative and fulfilling ways to thrive in your daily activities while staying aligned with your values.
title: "Finding Joy in Work: Blenders, Brussels, and Divine Interventions"
